<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Document</title>
  </head>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: "Lucida Sans", "Lucida Sans Regular", "Lucida Grande",
        "Lucida Sans Unicode", Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }
    a {
      color: grey;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    div {
      padding: 2px 20px;
      border: 1px solid grey;
      width: 100px;
      height: 50px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      border-radius: 10px;
      cursor: default;
    }
  </style>
  <body>
    <h1>[<%= userName %>] Verify Your Account with OTP</h1>
    <p>
      Enter this OTP below on our website to complete your registration. <br />
      This step is essential to confirm your identity [<%= email %>] <br />
      and secure your account.
    </p>
    <div><h1 style="cursor: default;"><%= otp %></h1></div>
    <p>
      Get ready to experience the convenience and joy of GiftACB. <br />
      Let's get started on this exciting gift card journey together!
    </p>
    <p>Click here to continue: <a href="<%= url %>"><%= url %></a></p>
  </body>
</html>
